  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Rural Enterprise Acceleration Project (REAP)</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The development objective is to increase levels of employment of rural populace through intensification of cluster based climate resilient production systems of select value chains and promotion of both farm and off-farm enterprise development through promotion of an ecosystem supportive to enterprise development.

The goal of Rural Enterprise Acceleration Project (REAP) is to contribute to the doubling of income of rural hill area households and reduce rural migration.</narrative>
  </description>
